<!-- Definition and symptoms -->
'''血友病'''多數是[[遺傳性疾病|遺傳性疾病]]，造成人體無法[[凝血|凝血]]形成血塊來[[止血|止血]]<ref name=NIH2013What>{{cite web|title=What Is Hemophilia?|url=https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hemophilia|website=NHLBI|accessdate=8 September 2016|date=July 13, 2013|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161004222515/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hemophilia|archivedate=2016-10-04|df=}}</ref><ref name=CDC2014>{{cite web|title=Hemophilia Facts|url=https://www.cdc.gov/ncbddd/hemophilia/facts.html|website=CDC|accessdate=8 September 2016|date=August 26, 2014|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827085015/http://www.cdc.gov/ncbddd/hemophilia/facts.html|archivedate=2016-08-27|df=}}</ref>。這致使病人受傷後[[流血|流血]]時間更長，易於[[淤青|淤青]]，和增加[[關節積血|關節積血]]或[[腦出血|腦出血]]的機率<ref name=NIH2013Sym/>。病情輕微的病人可能只有在意外或是手術時會有症狀<ref name=NIH2013Sym/>。關節內出血可能造成永久性的損傷，而腦出血可能造成長期的頭痛、癲癇、或是意識不清<ref name=NIH2013Sym>{{cite web|title=What Are the Signs and Symptoms of Hemophilia?|url=https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hemophilia/signs|website=NHLBI|accessdate=8 September 2016|date=July 13, 2013|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917105954/https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hemophilia/signs|archivedate=2016-09-17|df=}}</ref>。

<!-- Cause and mechanism -->
血友病可分為兩種主要的型別，{{le|血友病A型|Haemophilia A}}為缺乏{{le|第8凝血因子|Factor VIII}}，{{le|血友病B型|Haemophilia B}}為缺乏{{le|第9凝血因子|Factor IX}}<ref name=NIH2013What/>。血友病通常是因為來自父母不具功能的X染色體<ref name=NIH203Cau/>。很少數的血友病是因為發育過程中的新突變。血友病也有可能是因為使用抗生素後導致產生針對凝血因子的[[抗體|抗體]]<ref name=NIH2013What/><ref name=NIH203Cau>{{cite web|title=What Causes Hemophilia?|url=https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hemophilia/causes|website=NHLBI|accessdate=10 September 2016|date=July 13, 2013|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160908233612/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hemophilia/causes|archivedate=2016-09-08|df=}}</ref>。還有另外一種型式是{{le|血友病C型|Haemophilia C}}，是因為缺乏{{le|凝血因子11|Factor XI}}，[[副血友病|副血友病]]是因為缺乏{{le|凝血因子5|Factor V}}<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Franchini|first1=M|last2=Mannucci|first2=PM|title=Inhibitors of propagation of coagulation (factors VIII, IX and XI): a review of current therapeutic practice.|journal=British Journal of Clinical Pharmacology|date=October 2011|volume=72|issue=4|pages=553–62|pmid=21204915|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2125.2010.03899.x|pmc=3195733}}</ref><ref name=Thal2013>{{cite journal|last1=Thalji|first1=N|last2=Camire|first2=RM|title=Parahemophilia: new insights into factor v deficiency.|journal=Seminars in thrombosis and hemostasis|date=September 2013|volume=39|issue=6|pages=607–12|pmid=23893775|doi=10.1055/s-0033-1349224}}</ref> 。後天得到的血友病與[[癌症|癌症]]、[[自體免疫疾病|自體免疫疾病]]或[[懷孕|懷孕]]有關<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Franchini|first1=M|last2=Mannucci|first2=PM|title=Acquired haemophilia A: a 2013 update.|journal=Thrombosis and haemostasis|date=December 2013|volume=110|issue=6|pages=1114–20|pmid=24008306|doi=10.1160/TH13-05-0363}}</ref><ref name=Mul2014>{{cite journal|last1=Mulliez|first1=SM|last2=Vantilborgh|first2=A|last3=Devreese|first3=KM|title=Acquired hemophilia: a case report and review of the literature.|journal=International journal of laboratory hematology|date=June 2014|volume=36|issue=3|pages=398–407|pmid=24750687|doi=10.1111/ijlh.12210}}</ref>。透過測試凝血能力及凝血因子的濃度可診斷<ref name=NIH213Diag>{{cite web|title=How Is Hemophilia Diagnosed?|url=https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hemophilia/diagnosis|website=NHLBI|accessdate=10 September 2016|date=July 13, 2013|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915152750/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hemophilia/diagnosis|archivedate=2016-09-15|df=}}</ref>。

<!-- Prevention and treatment --> 
預防可透過取出卵子、使其受精，並在放回子宮前先行測試<ref name=NIH213Diag/>。給予缺乏的凝血因子為治療方式<ref name=CDC2014/>，可規律的施打或是在流血的時候給予<ref name=CDC2014/>。可以在醫院或是家中進行治療<ref name=NIH2013Tx/>。凝血因子可能是來自人血或是基因重組方式製造而得<ref name=NIH2013Tx>{{cite web|title=How Is Hemophilia Treated?|url=https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hemophilia/treatment|website=NHLBI|accessdate=10 September 2016|date=July 13, 2013|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917160609/https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/hemophilia/treatment|archivedate=2016-09-17|df=}}</ref>。大約20%的病人對凝血因子會產生抗體，使治療更加困難<ref name=CDC2014/>。醋酸去氨加壓素可用來治療輕微的血友病A型<ref name=NIH2013Tx/>。基因療法仍在進行早期的人體試驗<ref name=Pey2016>{{cite journal|last1=Peyvandi|first1=F|last2=Garagiola|first2=I|last3=Young|first3=G|title=The past and future of haemophilia: diagnosis, treatments, and its complications.|journal=Lancet|date=9 July 2016|volume=388|issue=10040|pages=187–97|pmid=26897598|doi=10.1016/s0140-6736(15)01123-x}}</ref>。

<!-- Epidemiology and culture -->
每5,000-10,000人中大約有1人受到血友病A型影響，而B型則為每40,000人中有1人<ref name=NIH2013What/><ref name=Wyn2009/> 。因為血友病A及B型為{{le|X染色體隱性遺傳|X-linked recessive inheritance}}，大部分的病患是男性<ref name=NIH203Cau/>。女性具有單一無功能X染色體可能具有些微的症狀<ref name=NIH203Cau/>。血友病C型在男女之間的發生率相同，且最常發生在[[阿什肯納茲猶太人|阿什肯納茲猶太人]]身上<ref name=Wyn2009/> 。在1800年代左右，血友病在歐洲皇室很常見<ref name=Wyn2009/> 。在1952年才發現血友病A與B型的不同<ref name=Wyn2009>{{cite book|last1=Wynbrandt|first1=James|last2=Ludman|first2=Mark D.|title=The Encyclopedia of Genetic Disorders and Birth Defects|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=kXaMjwItP0oC&pg=PA194|accessdate=25 August 2013|date=1 January 2009|publisher=Infobase Publishing|isbn=978-1-4381-2095-9|pages=194|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414055922/https://books.google.com/books?id=kXaMjwItP0oC&pg=PA194|archivedate=2021-04-14|df=}}</ref> 。血友病這個字是來自希臘文「haima αἷμα」，代表血和愛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?search=hemophilia&searchmode=none|title=Online Etymology Dictionary|author=Douglas Harper|accessdate=10 October 2007|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080306042235/http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?search=hemophilia&searchmode=none|archivedate=2008-03-06|df=}}</ref>。

== 致病机理 ==

正常的[[血液|血液]]凝结是血液中血小板，與部分血漿蛋白共同作用的结果。這些與凝血功能相關的血漿蛋白，即是[[凝血因子|凝血因子]]。由於凝血因子在血液凝固過程中，具有加速以及加強反應的效果，缺乏凝血因子的協助，就可能发生凝血功能異常，導致出血时间延长。血友病患者的凝血因子比正常人要少，因此血管破裂后，血液不容易凝固，导致出血难止。

按照患者所缺乏的凝血因子类型，可将最常見的血友病分为甲型、乙型、丙型三种（或是A型、B型、C型）。缺乏其他凝血因子的血友病，則無特殊分類，以缺乏的凝血因子來確認。
